query:
SELECT 
  o.orderNumber,
  o.orderDate,
  o.itemsCount,
  COUNT(s.id) as itens_em_sales
FROM orders o
LEFT JOIN sales s ON o.blingId = s.blingOrderId
WHERE o.orderDate >= '2024-09-01' 
  AND o.orderDate < '2024-10-01'
GROUP BY o.id, o.orderNumber, o.orderDate, o.itemsCount
HAVING itens_em_sales < itemsCount
LIMIT 10
